    <section id="faq" class="alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-h">
          <div class="eyebrow">FAQ</div>
          <h2>Things clubs ask before they order.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq" open>
            <summary>Do you need access to our Play Cricket?</summary>
            <p>
              No. We pull everything from the publicly available stats pages
              &mdash; you don't need to share any logins or passwords. Just
              tell us your club name and which XIs to include, and we handle
              the rest.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>How current are the stats?</summary>
            <p>
              On setup we pull every match from the last four seasons. During
              the season, we re-capture every Sunday night so Monday morning
              your URL is fresh.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>Can I include the junior section too?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes &mdash; Under-9 through Under-18 cricket can be added as a
              bolt-on for &pound;49. We add a separate "Junior" mode to the
              dashboard so seniors and juniors stay clearly separated.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>Who can see the URL?</summary>
            <p>
              Anyone you share it with &mdash; no login. Treat it like an
              unlisted YouTube video: not advertised, not indexed by Google, but
              viewable by anyone with the URL. If you'd rather have password
              protection, we offer that as a &pound;30 add-on.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>What's included in the &pound;99/year renewal?</summary>
            <p>
              Weekly stats refresh through every season, all new feature
              releases (we ship most weeks), continued hosting, and email
              support. If a season ends and you don't want to renew, the
              dashboard stops updating but stays live for the rest of the
              calendar year as a free archive.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary>What about T20s, midweek leagues, friendlies?</summary>
            <p>
              All competitions Play Cricket records show up &mdash; we let you
